      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Vivien Clauzon</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/tryingsomestuff\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/6/67/VivienClauzon.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:VivienClauzon.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Vivien Clauzon <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Vivien Clauzon</b>,<br />\na French software architect and applied mathematician holding a Ph.D. from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blaise_Pascal_University\">Clermont-Ferrand II</a> on the topic of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computational_fluid_dynamics\">computational fluid dynamics</a> in 2008.\nHe further elaborated on <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/L-stability\">L∞ stability</a> of the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MUSCL_scheme\">MUSCL method</a> in the study of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Partial_differential_equation\">partial differential equations</a>.\nAs a computer chess programmer, Vivien Clauzon is author of the chess engines <a href=\"/Weini\" title=\"Weini\">Weini</a> and <a href=\"/Minic\" title=\"Minic\">Minic</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2017\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2017</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2018\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2018</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2019\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2019</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2020\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2021\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2021</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vivien_Clauzon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i>Analyse de schémas d'ordre élevé pour les écoulements compressibles</i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blaise_Pascal_University\">Clermont-Ferrand II</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#TDubois\" title=\"Mathematician\">Thierry Dubois</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%2F978-90-481-3652-0_55\">Direct Numerical Simulation of Hot and Highly Pulsated Turbulent Jet Flows</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/book/10.1007/978-90-481-3652-0\">Direct and Large-Eddy Simulation VII</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=j5CJu4wAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Stéphane Clain</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>L∞ stability of the MUSCL methods</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Numerische_Mathematik\">Numerische Mathematik</a>, Vol. 116, No. 10 <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vivien_Clauzon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2017\">2017</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vivien_Clauzon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2017\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=65936\">Looking for advices</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 08, 2017</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=65936&amp;start=7\">Re: Looking for advices</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 25, 2018</dd></dl>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2018\">2018</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vivien_Clauzon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2018\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=67251\">About a rebel evaluation study</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 27, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=67455\">Root move sorting</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 15, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=67823\">Horizon effect and extensions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 25, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Horizon_Effect\" title=\"Horizon Effect\">Horizon Effect</a>, <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=67873\">MVV LVA</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 01, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/MVV-LVA\" title=\"MVV-LVA\">MVV/LVA</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=68081\">A question about futility prunning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 26, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Futility Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=68082\">Names of selectivity algorithms</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 26, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Selectivity\" title=\"Selectivity\">Selectivity</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=68290\">singular extension</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 24, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Singular_Extensions\" title=\"Singular Extensions\">Singular Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=68326\">Texel tuning speed</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 29, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Texel%27s_Tuning_Method\" title=\"Texel&#39;s Tuning Method\">Texel's Tuning Method</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=68701\">A complete 2000 lines of code engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 20, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Minic\" title=\"Minic\">Minic</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=68741\">very small bitboard move/attack generator</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 27, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=69438\">Bitboard question (from xiphos code)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 31, 2018</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2019\">2019</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vivien_Clauzon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2019\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=69966\">Singular extension ... again</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 19, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=70661\">(possible stupid question) asymmetrical search</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 04, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=70862\">Interior node recognizer and capture / stalemate</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 30, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Interior_Node_Recognizer\" title=\"Interior Node Recognizer\">Interior Node Recognizer</a>, <a href=\"/Stalemate\" title=\"Stalemate\">Stalemate</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=70938\">Using evaluation hash score as current bestscore (initial guess)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 06, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=71155\">Exchange</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 01, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=71205\">backward pawn</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 06, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Backward_Pawns_(Bitboards)\" title=\"Backward Pawns (Bitboards)\">Backward Pawns (Bitboards)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=71325\">Feature score use in search</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 20, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=71350\">Random mover win rate</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 24, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=71397\">Simplest use of syzygy table</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 28, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=71469\">Texel tuning Zurichess quiet like generato</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 06, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=71614\">PVS, window, and mate</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 20, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=71848\">self test</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 18, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Engine_Testing\" title=\"Engine Testing\">Engine Testing</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=71994\">Looking for TT policy advice</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 04, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table#ReplacementStrategies\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Replacement Strategy</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=72531\">CMH question</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 08, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/History_Heuristic#CMHist\" title=\"History Heuristic\">Counter Moves History</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=72686\">UCI pondering and time management</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 30, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a>, <a href=\"/Pondering\" title=\"Pondering\">Pondering</a>, <a href=\"/Time_Management\" title=\"Time Management\">Time Management</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020\">2020</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vivien_Clauzon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2020\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=72967\">Imbalance</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 01, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">Material</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=72981\">Pruning / reduction depending on king safety</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 02, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Pruning\" title=\"Pruning\">Pruning</a>, <a href=\"/Reductions\" title=\"Reductions\">Reductions</a>, <a href=\"/King_Safety\" title=\"King Safety\">King Safety</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=73521\">Minic version 2</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 31, 2020</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=73521&amp;start=59\">Re: Minic version 2</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 08, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a></dd></dl>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2021\">2021</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vivien_Clauzon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2021\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=76536\">Effect of adjudication and TC on testing process</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 09, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/Engine_Testing\" title=\"Engine Testing\">Engine Testing</a>, <a href=\"/Minic\" title=\"Minic\">Minic</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=76556\">HCE and NNUE and vectorisation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 11, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a>, <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a></li></ul>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vivien_Clauzon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://math.univ-bpclermont.fr/~clauzon/\">Vivien Clauzon  - Laboratoire de Mathématiques</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/vivien-clauzon-85635638/\">Vivien Clauzon | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/tryingsomestuff\">tryingsomestuff · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://500px.com/xr_a_y\">Vivien Clauzon (xr_a_y) Photos / 500px</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Vivien_Clauzon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/tryingsomestuff\">tryingsomestuff · GitHub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/c/Clauzon:Vivien\">dblp: Vivien Clauzon</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"